OL,3,CMan charged with murder of man at
OL,4,Csummer solstice event at stone circle
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murdering
OL,7,Fa young man who died at a summer
OL,8,Fsolstice event held at a stone circle
OL,9,Fin the Peak District.
OL,11,FIsaac Clare-Watts' body was discovered
OL,12,Fat the Nine Ladies Stone Circle in
OL,13,FStanton Lees, near Matlock, on Monday
OL,14,Fafternoon last week.
OL,16,FThe 26-year-old from Nottingham was
OL,17,Fsadly pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
