CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783521458
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of man at
OL,4,Csummer solstice event at stone circle
OL,6,FDerbyshire Police said on Monday that
OL,7,Fa man from London had since been
OL,8,Fcharged with Isaac's murder, as well
OL,9,Fas a second count of attempted murder
OL,10,Fover a separate incident in nearby
OL,11,FChesterfield.
OL,13,FPolish national Szymon Babynko of
OL,14,FCommonwealth Way, London, was arrested
OL,15,Fon Thursday over Isaac's murder.
OL,17,FHe will appear before Derby
OL,18,FMagistrates Court later today for
OL,19,Fmurder and a second count of attempted
OL,20,Fmurder in relation to the separate
OL,21,Fincident on Hady Lane, Chesterfield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
