FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783521458
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of man at
OL,4,Csummer solstice event at stone circle
OL,6,FBabynko, 23, was remanded into custody
OL,7,Fahead of the court appearance.
OL,9,FIn a previous statement, the Peak
OL,10,FDistrict National Park Authority said:
OL,11,F"We have been made aware of the tragic
OL,12,Fnews and the investigation is being
OL,13,Fhandled by our colleagues at the East
OL,14,FMidlands Special Operations Unit.
OL,16,F"Our condolences are with the young
OL,17,Fman's family during this difficult
OL,18,Ftime."
